ie.gmit.sw.Reflection

Interface Metricator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Metric

    public interface Metricator
    An Interface that contains all declarative methods required by the Metric class. This Abstraction was created with the purpose of providing an opportunity to create any desired implementation.
